::Shadow Wing::

She continued to wak around the inside of the ship.  She didn't like the 
idea of someone scanning her transmissions, especially when she didn't know 
who was scanning.  She walked around hoping to find someone who survived.  
She hoped that Lunarpine was alright where ever he was.  He hoped he didn't 
run into trouble out there.
